@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Chat API" as API
participant "LLM Provider" as LLM
database PostgreSQL

User -> Frontend: Gui cau hoi
Frontend -> API: POST /api/chat/sessions/:id/messages
API -> PostgreSQL: save user message
API -> LLM: completion request
LLM --> API: assistant answer
API -> PostgreSQL: save assistant message
API --> Frontend: response + metadata
Frontend --> User: Hien thi cau tra loi
@enduml
